title: 871. Shift of Offense to Defense & Layup TD Leaders
itunes:title: 871. Shift of Offense to Defense & Layup TD Leaders
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys look at the shift of offense to defense as the NFL is on track for its worst offensive season in 5 years. Next, the pair discuss the layup touchdown leaders, which are defined by inside 3-yard line touchdown passes. Then, the duo break down the battle of the Bills and Chiefs offenses in their Week 6 matchup. To wrap up the show, the guys hit on the top 5 sack leaders this season.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
